{
  "stem": "11964.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Polish people were, unfortunately-- and I must say that because that is the truth-- the Polish people were not, not kindly disposed towards Jews.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were, they were really anti-Semitic, simply because it was ingrained in them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The truth of the matter is, that unfortunately, it was the Christian religion that really did that indoctrination.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Those of us who know the Gospels would know that if you teach the gospel, if you read John or Matthew, you just straight understand.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You-- there is a straight line.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jews are not of God the Father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They are of their father, the devil.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And these things were [? encalculated ?] into them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, this was simply a brainwashing system of preaching to the Jews, that Jews were responsible for the deicide, for the murder of Christ.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they held it over our heads all the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I must say that we, we, we encountered some very good exceptions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One exception was a judge in town who was a good friend of my father's, and who, eventually, really, is responsible for saving all three of us after he had found out that my mother and father were taken away.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was also one woman who was very fond of my mother, a Christian, who tried to help me out very, very much, and who would come to the ghetto, and who would bring me some food occasionally.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the majority of the Polish population, who were very, very Catholic and Christian, would not be very, very kindly disposed.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
